{"tid":2184616,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"第二期保就業計劃接獲近九萬申請","createTime":"2020-09-01T16:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T16:22:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b5819d2a4bd699b0991c2675b0dad7ca73f63ac0","tid":2184616,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/09/20200901/20200901_190433_082.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F09%2F20200901%2F20200901_190433_082.html&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYaRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=004a769d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/09/20200901/20200901_190433_082.html</a><br />\n<br />\n政府表示，保就業計劃第二期昨日開始接受申請，截至今日傍晚6時收到約83,000名僱主和逾6,000名自僱人士的申請，其中約95%成功申請第一期保就業計劃。<br />\n<br />\n保就業計劃第二期工資補貼申請本月13日晚上11時59分截止。政府會迅速處理申請，預計在接獲申請後三至四星期向大部分獲批者發放工資補貼。<br />\n<br />\n保就業計劃秘書處會通過電郵和手機短信通知成功申請者，他們可登入保就業計劃網頁，查閱獲批的補貼金額和承諾於9月至11月的受薪僱員人數。 <br />\n<br />\n自僱人士如已開設自僱人士強積金戶口，並在3月31日仍未取消，兼不曾在保就業計劃第一期獲得一筆過7,500元資助，也可申領第二期工資補貼。"},{"pid":"8e33ed491c55c15bdf4a824d1c328f18e254356a","tid":2184616,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"約83,000名僱主和逾6,000名自僱人士<br />\n<br />\n關我失業撚 撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}